Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:57.54,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}想要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在這裡  某種等級以上的鬼兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用武器是無法打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能…教我劍術呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…你要活下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我要活著去做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會死  而是不能死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺了想來殺我的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:03:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會殺死想要奪走我已經決定保護的東西的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也記不清我到底打倒了多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想說什麼漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明氣數未盡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自己卻不想活的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這世上我最討厭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最討厭的類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑磷做的早飯好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼說也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全與開店的氣氛不合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑碰他們要到哪裡去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要完成必須做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向黑狗狗學習劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狗狗們的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忘記帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是法伊先生要我拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「中午飯吃這個就好」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早  是要去那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼是要向黑狗狗學習劍術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是為了完成必須做的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是尋找公主散落的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要買劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是正式登記的鬼兒獵人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那個  我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你要的話…這把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該已經用慣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  因為我做這行很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍的名字是「蒼冰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼冰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那邊那位應該沒有使劍的經驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼中充滿火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征一  把那個拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說  是他的巧斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我們認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很溫順
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話也許可以駕馭它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫「緋炎」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋炎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕緊付帳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  還真是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可先說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會打折的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那個老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真的一點都不打折呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我對刀劍不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是知道這是一把很棒的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到時機成熟時才能出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀劍是不會選擇對象的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用劍的人不夠成熟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的刀鋒也會跟著不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會把不需要斬殺的人也給斬殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如你該保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你能夠斬殺應該要斬殺的對象為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別解開它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要拔出它所該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請在這裡簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像在哪裡見過這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  多謝惠顧～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件樂器叫做「鋼琴」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小路裡的琴行看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時興起  就買下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊會彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很有開店氣氛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊  你還是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法取得左右反應的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼無論如何就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對於來自右方的反應確實慢了點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有時候有時候只根據「氣息」來行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會比左方的反應更快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的左眼太過於依賴視力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不首先掌握左右平衡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就無法使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕套餐兩份對吧？我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我要點菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻還是一樣很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻真偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥草茶…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感覺到和呼喚著這個世界的聲音的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所擁有的相同的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然  這是傳言中的那個餐館嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我說兩句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你在收集傳說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在收集和這個國家的改變有關的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不可思議的事件之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您們知道些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  小櫻也開始做自己該做的事情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集和羽毛相關的情報哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該是自己為此努力的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也緊張起來了呢  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您知道些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  好像很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是…因為找到該做的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要依賴視覺  用心來感受「氣息」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去市役所把這個換掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是法伊先生的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我會去看下醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你們兩個看店了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  法伊先生也請路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉啊轉  轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在寫歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能借我用用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的鋼琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是用作裝飾太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…「小小的貓咪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的不是在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那麼  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我聽聽你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  因為這裡是櫻都國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲是可以映出一個人的全部的鏡子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪裡來的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後打算去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言最重要的是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情我已經很清楚了  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著和你再次相遇的那一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位看店辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿白天睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回…小狼君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼全身都是傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又遇見鬼兒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  啊…我去換件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻真是努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一會兒  就讓他們這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識別編號NDC726191P
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認的名字是  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對解任者直接的設定不予承認
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後  依照通常設定進行計測
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在修練的小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和龍王再次見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.38,0:24:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑碰和法伊則是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.46,0:24:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迷一般的歌姬那裡收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.88,0:24:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在這時候  小櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  你想要去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？新種的鬼兒終於出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的真面目是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.06,0:24:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請繼續期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.86,0:24:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代記  第二十一話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.37,0:24:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼兒的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.50,0:24:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的黑鋼去買東西讓人期待不已


